data.description: Indulge in the perfect blend of nature and modern living with this beautiful home with South Umpqua River Frontage. The open living area and spacious kitchen create a welcoming atmosphere, leading to a covered stamped concrete patio for relaxation and entertainment. You'll appreciate the convenience of the paved driveway with RV electrical hook-ups beside the garage ensuring hassle-free parking. An oversized hickory shed makes the perfect workshop with power. For gardening enthusiasts, a 50ft x 100ft fenced garden area with a greenhouse and chicken run awaits, providing the perfect space for your green thumb to flourish. Embrace a serene and practical lifestyle in this river side haven. Contact us now to make this your new home!
